Broadcasters.
The Jazz's flagship radio stations are KZNS (1280) "The Zone" and KZNS-FM Fox Sports Radio 97.5.
The Jazz signed a new exclusive 12-year agreement with Root Sports Utah on October 20, 2009, ending the team's broadcasts on KJZZ-TV.
The team's current TV and radio announcers are:
